teetime.stage.taskfarm

Class DynamicTaskFarmStage<I,O,T extends ITaskFarmDuplicable<I,O>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.CompositeStage
      • teetime.stage.taskfarm.StaticTaskFarmStage<I,O,T>
        • teetime.stage.taskfarm.DynamicTaskFarmStage<I,O,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - Input type of task Farm
    O - Output type of task Farm
    T - Type of the parallelized stage
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITransformation<I,O>

    public class DynamicTaskFarmStage<I,O,T extends ITaskFarmDuplicable<I,O>>
extends StaticTaskFarmStage<I,O,T>
    Represents the self-adaptive task farm parallelization pattern in TeeTime. It dynamically adds CPU resources at runtime depending on the current CPU load and the behavior of the parallelized stage.
    Author:
    Christian Claus Wiechmann, Christoph Dornieden
